data.description: **ASSUMABLE LOAN FOR QUALIFIED BUYER WITH 5.25% RATE**1% CASH BACK of the loan amount *up to $7000* in LENDER CREDIT to be applied towards closing costs with using preferred lender. Discover your dream home nestled in the tranquil hill country surroundings of West San Antonio! This stunning property offers a perfect balance between serene natural beauty and convenient city living. Step inside and be greeted by the bright and spacious interior of this magnificent residence. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a large loft area, and a media room upstairs, there is ample space for your household to spread out and relax. The floor plan's layout allows for easy transitions between rooms, providing both privacy and social options. Indulge in the ultimate entertainment experience with the dedicated media room, where you can enjoy movie nights with friends and loved ones. On the covered back patio, imagine sipping your morning coffee and listening to the gentle sounds of nature. Located in West San Antonio, you'll have access to the main city while still relishing the tranquility of hill country living. Whether you're exploring nearby hiking trails, shopping at local boutiques, or dining at charming restaurants, you'll appreciate the perfect blend of convenience and natural beauty that this location offers. Don't miss the opportunity to call this remarkable property your own and experience the best of both worlds in West San Antonio. Schedule a showing today and let this exceptional home become your personal haven.
